{
  "stem": "214.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So, it was-- actually, my parents probably wouldn't be very happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You know, I didn't date before.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was-- we were supposed to be Hasidic girls.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You probably know that, or maybe you don't know that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It's difficult to imagine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You did not date.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but-- but-- that's what maybe he meant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We started, you know, seeing each other, and he was writing me little notes, and we were sometimes-- you know, I'm going to [INAUDIBLE], he was there too, and a few other young boys, and all the young girls.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that's how we-- that's how we met.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we never thought of getting married now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were-- we were going to get married after the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sorry-- by asking you about Benno, but-- what we missed was what happened to your-- what happened when the Germans invaded Poland?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We kind of skipped over that part of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, if you don't mind, can we go back and can you tell me what happened to-- in Lodz, and anything you might have witnessed once the Germans came into Lodz?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- well, one could say with one word, it was really bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I remember first of all, you know, every day, there was new rules and regulations promulgated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they were about was-- I mean, there was hardly any-- but-- but this maybe also has to do something with the war conditions-- there was no bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Unless you had something prepared before, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember my aunt, that same fellow-- what was his name?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Tsikovsky or whatever.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He would bring us something from-- from Skierniewice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "A chicken-- which was a kosher chicken, kosher slaughtered-- or a dozen of eggs.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
